                             LOW = as.numeric(LOW$LOW.Adjusted))

                             id.vars = c('Date'),
                             measure.vars = c('HD', 'LOW'),
                             variable.name = 'Stock',
                             value.name = 'Price')

              y = ~Price, color = ~Stock,
